    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/6f1b78c56cc9c12cfb5f2596edbf763f.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=336 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2>这是一款文字冒险游戏，玩家将通过推理和对话寻找罪犯。<br>游戏系统基于新的模拟游戏类型 &quot;谋杀之谜&quot;。<br>即使您从未玩过 &quot;谋杀推理 &quot;游戏，也可以尽情享受游戏的乐趣。<br>通关游戏大约需要 10 个小时。<br>游戏有多个结局，结局的分支取决于玩家的选择。<br>当玩家陷入谜团时，有丰富的提示指引。<br>游戏提供试玩版，玩家可以试玩游戏的前几个小时。 跳过试玩版即可玩完整版游戏。<br>整个游戏可供下载。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏概述</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/7a4bc21a01c40ecb877ce1d6f4e8e6da.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=336 /></span>.<br><br><strong>&quot;罪魁祸首就在这里！&quot; </strong><br><br>您参与了在封闭环境中寻找事件元凶的行动。 然而，你自己也是嫌疑人之一，并被其他人怀疑。<br><br>在有限的时间内，您要通过与嫌疑人的对话收集案件线索，并从中推理出真相。 与此同时，你还需要获得周围人的信任，以洗清自己的嫌疑。<br><br>如果你最终没有足够的可信度，就可能成为罪魁祸首......。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■游戏系统</h2>寻找罪魁祸首的神秘部分按照以下顺序进行：&quot;调查阶段 → 一般性讨论阶段 → 投票阶段&quot;。<br><br><strong>调查阶段</strong><br>通过与嫌疑人一对一的秘密谈话，了解案件的相关信息和问题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/23ab9298851e06b2ee2125eab451d7bd.poster.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/23ab9298851e06b2ee2125eab451d7bd.webm?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/23ab9298851e06b2ee2125eab451d7bd.mp4?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过在对话中提供信息和回答问题，玩家可以获得对方的信任，从而查清案件的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/d67938b18f1e6afdf77712fb29802135.poster.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/d67938b18f1e6afdf77712fb29802135.webm?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/d67938b18f1e6afdf77712fb29802135.mp4?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/60bc68eae0e961e200f4d70b3a938c76.poster.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/60bc68eae0e961e200f4d70b3a938c76.webm?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/60bc68eae0e961e200f4d70b3a938c76.mp4?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>一般性讨论阶段</strong><br>在调查阶段，每个嫌疑人都将依次陈述他们对案件和罪犯的推断。 你同意谁的说法，否认谁的说法，这取决于你自己的可信度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/e140ad9c16a47df686ee3d5479033846.poster.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/e140ad9c16a47df686ee3d5479033846.webm?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/e140ad9c16a47df686ee3d5479033846.mp4?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>投票阶段</strong><br>根据在调查阶段和一般性讨论阶段获得的信息，每个嫌疑人都会投票给他们认为是罪魁祸首的人。 得票数最高的人将被您拘留为犯人。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/cb0b844c4dfac52f09a717495f39d330.poster.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/cb0b844c4dfac52f09a717495f39d330.webm?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/cb0b844c4dfac52f09a717495f39d330.mp4?t=1729483872\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■故事梗概</h2>2004 年 8 月。<br>志庆岛，一个只有几百人口的偏远小岛。<br>今年夏天，15 岁的男孩 &quot;天泽辰 &quot;第一次来到志庆岛。<br>在养母家，他见到了没有血缘关系的表兄弟，并与他们度过了一段平静的时光。<br><br>此时的辰木还不知道。<br>他还不知道，一个被称为 &quot;敷音岛的神乐 &quot;的神秘事件已经在岛上反复发生。<br>而他所关心的人也深深地卷入了这起案件的谜团之中。<br><br>大树能否揭开神秘事件背后的真相，拯救他所关心的人.......。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203040/extras/f8497c678f40ba830f01776d9007b4df.avif?t=1729483872\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br> <br> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■交付指南</h2>[2024 年 3 月 1 日修订]<br>在传播有关影片的视频时，现在可以传播影片的全部内容。<br>为了确保尽可能多的观众能够欣赏到影片，在传播含有剧透的内容时，请在标题中明确指出该内容含有剧透。",
